title: NeonFace Watchface
summary: A moody neon-themed throwback for your wrist!
description: What's cooler than a neon-themed watchface in 2017?Well, probably a lot of things. Explosions for one thing.But you can't get those on the Play Store if you don't own a Note7.So, this is the next coolest thing!
descriptionHTML:
What's cooler than a neon-themed watchface in 2017?
Well, probably a lot of things.
Explosions for one thing.
But you can't get those on the Play Store if you don't own a Note7.
So, this is the next coolest thing!
recentChanges: Fixed a scaling issue on flat tired watches (looking at you, moto)
